Description_lang: Your harmful spells and abilities have a low chance to call upon tragic arcane powers to infect your target with Crystal Sickness, dealing ${($s1*$433522d/$433522t1*$433522u)/2} Arcane damage over $433522d, increasing every second. Creatures, other than players and bosses, who drop below $s2% health while afflicted will crystallize, die and infect a nearby enemy with Crystal Sickness. This can happen up to $s4 times.
